Flyxion doesn't claim to have solved the biological origin of subjective experience, why the lights are on at all,

56:13.720 --> 56:19.640
but they offer a compelling geometric description of what consciousness is when it occurs.

56:19.640 --> 56:22.460
How do you describe human consciousness geometrically?

56:22.980 --> 56:33.480
The paper speculates that what we perceive as a unified conscious state is simply a trajectory through the representational manifold that is exceptionally stable,

56:34.480 --> 56:40.980
possesses extremely low entropy, and maintains incredibly high phase alignment over time.

56:41.200 --> 56:42.900
So it's a perfectly stable path.

56:42.900 --> 56:48.180
Conscious states are the specific paths that perfectly satisfy the biological prior,

